You should submit links to the posts in this assignment. 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;•  A good way to test the accuracy of the link is to copy and paste it into an "incognito" browsing session

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;• Please leave links to the posts in the WRITE SUBMISSION portion of the Blackboard submission, not the COMMENTS section

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;• Please do not number your posts; three links is sufficient (and preferred)

